{"type":"message","id":"d57d0520","parentId":"2f077ab1","timestamp":"2026-03-03T00:52:24.395Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"  functions.read:26","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2026-03-01 07:06:22 +08] Starting daily ping job...\n[2026-03-01 07:06:22 +08] Log file: /home/project/openclaw/logs/daily-ping-2026-03-01.log\n[2026-03-01 07:06:22 +08] Fetching Bitcoin data from CoinGecko...\n[2026-03-01 07:06:22 +08] Bitcoin: 67121 (change: 2.1961476435489944%)\n[2026-03-01 07:06:22 +08] Fetching GitHub data...\n[2026-03-01 07:06:23 +08] GitHub data fetched successfully\n[2026-03-01 07:06:23 +08] Fetching stock data (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD)...\n{\"NVDA\": {\"price\": 177.19, \"change_pct\": -4.16464, \"company\": \"NVIDIA Corporation\"}, \"MSFT\": {\"price\": 392.74, \"change_pct\": -2.2353907, \"company\": \"Microsoft Corporation\"}, \"GOOGL\": {\"price\": 311.76, \"change_pct\": 1.42495, \"company\": \"Alphabet Inc.\"}, \"INTC\": {\"price\": 45.61, \"change_pct\": 0.32996377, \"company\": \"Intel Corporation\"}, \"META\": {\"price\": 648.18, \"change_pct\": -1.34397, \"company\": \"Meta Platforms, Inc.\"}, \"AMD\": {\"price\": 200.21, \"change_pct\": -1.7036461, \"company\": \"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\"}}\n[2026-03-01 07:06:27 +08] Stock data fetched successfully\n[2026-03-01 07:06:27 +08] Daily ping job completed\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772499144391}}
