{"type":"message","id":"d3b692e9","parentId":"d3e5c3ac","timestamp":"2026-03-03T00:58:24.610Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"                   functions.read:40","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-ping-telegram\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1770773359648,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772493300093,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 7 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Singapore\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Execute the daily ping using existing infrastructure at /home/project/openclaw/:\\n\\n1. Run /home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh to fetch data with modified GitHub query for TRENDING repos (not just top stars)\\n2. Run /home/project/openclaw/generate-daily-message.sh to create the formatted message\\n3. Send the message via Telegram to 1087368827\\n\\nIMPORTANT MODIFICATIONS to make before running:\\n- Update the GitHub API URL in daily-ping-cron.sh to fetch TRENDING instead of top stars:\\n  OLD: https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=stars:>1000&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=5\\n  NEW: https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=created:>2024-01-01&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=10\\n- Update the message format in generate-daily-message.sh to match your preferred format with 📈📉 indicators\\n- Format stars as K (e.g., 148K instead of 148045)\\n\\nIf the shell scripts fail, use Python directly via /home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-sender.py\\n\\nTimeout: 15 minutes (900 seconds)\",\n        \"thinking\": \"low\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772578800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772492400057,\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 900036,\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 14,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772499504605}}
