{"type":"message","id":"218ef25a","parentId":"eb1ba62c","timestamp":"2026-03-03T04:39:27.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"  functions.read:90","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-02-25 - Daily Notes\n\n## Afternoon\n\n### 17:43 PM — Memory System Review & Update\n\n**Task:** Comprehensive review of QMD hierarchical memory system\n\nFindings:\n- QMD fully operational (v1.0.6)\n- 5 collections configured: system, daily, reference, skills, projects\n- MCP server running on localhost:8181\n- **Issue:** No automatic daily index updates (cron job missing)\n- **Issue:** Daily files indexed but stale (last update 7 days ago, Feb 18)\n- **Issue:** AGENTS.md still references old flat path `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\nActions Taken:\n- Created this daily memory file in new hierarchical structure\n- Updated AGENTS.md to reference new `memory/daily/YYYY/MM/DD.md` format\n- Added QMD daily update cron job\n- Re-indexed all collections\n\n**Verified:** QMD query test returned results from daily/ collection\n- `qmd query \"cron job gateway token\" -c daily` → returned Feb 18 notes\n- System functional, but automation gap discovered and fixed\n\n---\n\n### 17:49 PM — AGENTS.md Update\n\nRewrote the memory workflow section:\n- Old: Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- New: Read `memory/daily/YYYY/MM/DD.md` (today + yesterday)\n\n**Migration needed:** Move legacy flat files to new structure:\n- `2026-02-01.md` → `daily/2026/02/01.md`\n- `2026-02-09.md` → `daily/2026/02/09.md`  \n- `2026-02-10.md` → `daily/2026/02/10.md`\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Memory System Status:** ✅ OPERATIONAL (with fixes applied)\n\n**Key Files:**\n- QMD Config: `~/.config/qmd/index.yml`\n- Daily Notes Path: `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/YYYY/MM/DD.md`\n- Reference Docs: `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/reference/`\n- Update Script: `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/qmd-daily-update.sh`\n\n**Automation Added:**\n- Cron: `30 3 * * *` for `qmd-daily-update.sh` (3:30 AM daily)\n\n**Next Maintenance:** \n- Monitor daily index updates\n- Migrate remaining flat daily files to hierarchical structure\n- Weekly review: sync MEMORY.md with daily insights (per AGENTS.md protocol)\n\n*Recording complete. Memory system operational.* 🦞\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772512767139}}
